<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Feedback Form</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f0f2f5;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .feedback-form {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stars {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 5px;
            direction: rtl; /* Set direction to RTL */
            font-size: 2em; /* Ensure font size is applied correctly */
        }
        .stars input {
            display: none;
        }
        .stars label {
            color: #ccc;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .stars input:checked ~ label,
        .stars input:checked ~ label ~ label {
            color: #f39c12;
        }
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            height:100px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 2px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            resize: vertical;
        }
        button {
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <form action="">
    <div class="feedback-form">
        <h2>Rate your experience</h2>
        <p>We highly value your feedback! Kindly take a moment to rate your experience and provide us with your valuable feedback.</p>
        <div class="stars">
            <input type="radio" id="star5" name="rating" value="5" /><label for="star5">★</label>
            <input type="radio" id="star4" name="rating" value="4" /><label for="star4">★</label>
            <input type="radio" id="star3" name="rating" value="3" /><label for="star3">★</label>
            <input type="radio" id="star2" name="rating" value="2" /><label for="star2">★</label>
            <input type="radio" id="star1" name="rating" value="1" /><label for="star1">★</label>
        </div>
        <textarea rows="4" placeholder="Tell us about your experience"></textarea>
        <button type="submit">Send</button>
    </div>
</form>
</body>
</html>
